Subject: [PATCH 5/6] FIX: add missing 't' dependency to App.tsx useEffect

- FIX: format App.tsx in embed.ironcalc.com
- FIX: use optional chaining in usePointer.ts
- FIX: resolve infinite loop and memory leak in App.tsx
  - Use initialization guard in useEffect to prevent infinite loop with 't' and 'i18n' dependencies.
  - Wrap model saving setInterval in useEffect with cleanup to prevent memory leaks.

Signed-off-by: phanirithvij <phanirithvij2000@gmail.com>
